.TH "vmcoredd_update_size" 9 "vmcoredd_update_size" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
vmcoredd_update_size \- Update the total size of the device dumps and update Elf header
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" vmcoredd_update_size
.BI "(size_t dump_size "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dump_size" 12
Size of the current device dump to be added to total size
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Update the total size of all the device dumps and update the Elf program
headers. Calculate the new offsets for the vmcore list and update the
total vmcore size.
